data.description: Step into this unique 8-acre country home, where inviting front and back porches welcome you. Revel in 5 spacious bedrooms each with a walk-in closet. The master bathroom entices with a double vanity sink, oversized tub, walk-in tile shower and a private toilet room. Hardwood floors grace the living room and kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and a breakfast bar island. Satisfy culinary desires with a roomy pantry and enjoy the spacious laundry room with backyard access. Although home is ran with central heating, wall heaters stand by ready for emergencies. Outside, a carport and a 2 car garage with an extra bay await housing a den with a bar. Explore further to discover a 14-bay professional kennel, two nurseries, and a covered indoor training arena. Additional storage is provided by two outbuildings. Conveniently located minutes away from town and an hour away from Atlanta, this home opens doors to endless possibilities.
